# An interpreted, interactive, object-oriented programming language
dev-lang/python doc examples gdbm -hardened ipv6 ncurses readline sqlite ssl threads -tk wide-unicode wininst xml

# build 	INTERNAL USE ONLY!
# doc		Add extra documentation (API, Javadoc, etc)
# examples	Install examples, usually sourcecode
# gdbm		Add support for GNU databases libraries
# hardened	Activate default security enhancements for toolchain (gcc, glibc, binutils)
# ipv6		Add support for ipv6
# ncurses	Add ncurses support 
# readline	Enable support for GNU line-editing library (everybody want's this!!!!)
# squlite	Add support for sqlite !!! Firefox needs this !!!
# ssl		Add support for Secure Sockets Layer
# threads	Enable threading support (!!! SHOULD NOT BE DISABLED !!!)
# tk		Add support for Tk GUI toolkit
# wide-unicode	DONT DISABLE THIS
# wininst	Install Windows executables required to create exe-installer for Windows
# xml		Add xml support
